originalText.text: Technical and medical experience and talent ,mixed with compassion.  Having cancer treatment during Covid pandemic was even more difficult. Dr. Feldman and his team saw us through. Highly recommend if you think a family member has cancer go to MSK FIRST !. And no matter where you are only go to NCI (Natl.Cancer Inst) hospitals. don't start local -  go to the experts at MSK first and give yourself the best chance of success. The expertise of the doctors and nurses along with the compassion from support staff from meals to parking attendants makes the journey so much easier.
